            <h1>2.1 Keyboard Accessibility</h1>

            <p class="Info">Web content should be designed in a way that allows the users to navigate and interact
             with it effectively.</p>
            <p class"Info"> Give non-text content a descriptive text alternative and if its complex add on a meaningful caption. </p>

            <br>


            <p class"Info"> All functionality should be able to be operable through a keyboard interface
             without requiring specific timings for individual keystrokes.</p>

            <br>


            <p class"Info">Its important to make sure keyboard focus is visible and indicates the element that
            currently has focus.</p>

            </section>
            <section>
