            <p class="Info"> There should be enough time for the users to read and use content.
            If the content is time based, provide user controls to adjust or extend the time limits.</p>
            <br>

            <p class="Info"> Have a option for users to turn off or adjust any time limits for content that
            updates or scrolls automatically. </p>

